 📱 Social Media Checklist 

 Do’s

-> Use strong and unique passwords for all accounts
-> Enable two-factor authentication (2FA)
-> Keep your profiles private when needed
-> Think before you post — digital footprint matters
-> Verify information before sharing (avoid fake news)
-> Accept requests only from people you know
-> Use secure networks while logging in
-> Regularly update your privacy settings

 Don’ts

-> Don’t share personal information (address, phone, passwords)
-> Don’t click on suspicious links or unknown emails
-> Don’t accept unknown friend/follow requests
-> Don’t post content that is offensive or harmful
-> Don’t overshare your location or daily routine
-> Don’t reuse the same password everywhere
-> Don’t ignore security alerts or warnings
-> Don’t trust everything you see online
